Artists

Overview

There are 15,243 different artists in the MoMa data set. They and their unique characteristics are listed in a single file, Artists.csv

77 of these artists have a name identical to that of another artist in the dataset. Many of these are ‘Unidentified’. The others, in most cases, appear to be father and son.

Nationality

There are 120 different artist nationalities. There are 2,472 artists for whom a nationality is not given

Artist Birth Year

Most artists are born in the 20th century. There are 3,642 artists for whom a birth year is not given.

Gender

Most artists are male. There are 3,165 artists for whom a gender is not given.
